Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Outcast's Dream!\NHiriluk the Quack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day 3. Prognosis, the\Nbacteria were reduced to 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you'd expect from a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what happens if I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke, poke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you become my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really really like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in pirates at all.\NAnd I never wanted a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you become my friend,\Nmy other friends will all be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I wanna\Nbecome your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely make\Nyou become my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for you to get\Na healthy smile back,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared an exceptionally\Nnutritious dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though you're still painfully beautiful\Neven after what your body's been through...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lord! When did you use\Nmy kitchen without asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, the roast over there is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's high in protein and is\Ngood for rejuvena-- Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a "madam."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a sparkling single...\Nand still youthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still 139 years old... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctorine! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's gonna join us\Nand become our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend, huh? How deep a\Nmeaning that word has to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To ask without knowing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one man whom he opened\Nup to when he was alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man's name was Dr. Hiriluk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a quack who gave Chopper\Na name and called him son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We can't find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn quack, Hiriluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch him no matter what!\NThose're Wapol-sama's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes sir!\N--Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go on like this.\NLet's call a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. There aren't any doctors\Nin this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for the Twenty MDs who\Nbelong exclusively to Wapol...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll beg Wapol and call\Nthe Twenty MDs. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll examine him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiriluk! N-no thank you!\NPlease don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of people you treated\Nended up getting worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be modest. I just developed a\Nwonderful all-purpose drug yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? It's not what you think.\NThis is a tranquilizer gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use it when the\Npatient's pain is severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm gonna go get the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave!\NIf you want money, I'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't take money from sick people.\NI just want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Stop it! I've got a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Croak! Croak, croak!\NCroak, croak, croak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Croak! Croak!\NCroak, croak! Croak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? This is strange.\NDid I use a wrong ingredient?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought frog extract would work...\NGuess it was a failure. Oh man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry... I didn't\Nmean for this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiriluk! Are you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold it!\N--Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor hunt has come\Nto the final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that you and I are the\Nonly doctors left in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol is trying desperately to catch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that wasn't the case, you're\Nalready an outcast in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you're the worst of the quacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get caught by some doctor hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save this country using\Nmedical science one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Didn't you mean to say\N"destroy the country"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're people on the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you around, quack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna see you again,\Nyou thieving doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save as many sick people as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been shot? We need to stop\Nthe bleeding right away or you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a yeti! Shoot him to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made an ointment that even\Nworks on broken bones 3 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?\NYou don't look like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. You're that yeti that\Npeople have been talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't enough! Finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H... How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think... I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Dr. Hiriluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Chopper and Hiriluk's\Nfirst encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened... to the\Nreindeer taken in by Hiriluk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You can talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stay quiet for 3 days?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd hate me if I talked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I talked to humans the\Nother day, they shot me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it's strange for\Na reindeer to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You speak, so what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can speak, too...\Na lot better than you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! It failed again!\NHey, are you okay, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Well, you aren't okay\Nto start with, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you calling me Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Tony Tony Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're a reindeer and have\Nfine antlers that could chop down trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cool name, isn't it?\NThat's what I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Chopper. Always observe patients,\Nand give them proper treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing so will save people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Patients are waiting\Nfor me today once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought lizard eyeballs would work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! It's the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! We'll use the decoy plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost got me killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?! You failed to die once already!\NYou clumsy blue nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me blue nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the first time\NI've fought with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense... To fight,\Nyou have to have an opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... is it your first time\Nfor this as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you. It's a gift...\Nas a memento of our making up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gift? Making up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both go through hardships\Nas outcasts, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't hold a grudge against humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is sick right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the citizens and the king\Nsuffer from a sickness of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People would probably say that\Nyou can't treat a sick country,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once my invention is complete,\Nthis country will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There used to be a master-thief\Nin a country in the far west.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a serious heart disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to see every possible skilled\Ndoctor and got treated by them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no one was able to cure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being told he'd die,\Nhe passed by a mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while frustrated and unsettled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There... he saw a sight that\Nhe had never seen in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms! He saw vivid\Ncherry blossoms all over the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, he went to see another\Ndoctor and was shocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he was told...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're completely healthy."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was cured! It was indeed\Na miracle! Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this was unmistakably medical science!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By being emotionally moved, some sort\Nof change happened in this man's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there's no disease\Nin this world that can't be cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says about me,\NI'll save this country as a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I raised this skull\Ntowards all the diseases!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a symbol of the belief\Nthat nothing is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save this country as a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By raising this,\NI'll fight just like pirates do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join us and become our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Whoa! That looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool to be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, what are pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are incredible guys at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have large, well-trained\Nbodies and eyes like an eagle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their voices are like\Na thunder splitting the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... really a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I've been saying, join us!\NIt's fun to be a pirate! Pirates sing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Th-they sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And they dance, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that being a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!\NAnd they go on lots of adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adventures? So pirates\Ngo on adventures then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Pirates risk their\Nlives to go on adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can meet lots of amazing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool to be a pirate!\NThere're tons of incredible guys at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, go out to sea some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, you'll understand very\Nwell how small your problems are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island that you were born on\Nis like this compared to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's smaller! Like this! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your future lies beyond that sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The good times passed in the\Ntwinkling of an eye... And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time to bid farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,comes for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took one year.\NNow your treatment is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your injuries are\Ncompletely healed, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then... take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, leave! Live as you please!\NI'm busy with my research!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have any moral\Nobligation to take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! I'll never cause you\Nany trouble! Please let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll massage your shoulders everyday!\NI'll make you tea and clean the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Let me stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any friends!\NI have no place to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Doctor.\NI'm injured. Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go... to the sea! Go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna... die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! How many more days do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? If you're asking me\Nto examine you, I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the money to pay my fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill a person\Nwith a tranquilizer gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you. You'll die at 5 pm\Non the 10th day from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have to suffer any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 days... That'll be enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 2 days... In 2 days, I'll complete the\Nresearch I've continued for 30 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will... make cherry blossoms\Nbloom in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms? So the research\Nyou've continued for 30 years
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was about making cherry blossoms bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The miracle cherry blossoms that\Nsaved you, a master thief, long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool. This is a winter island\Nwhere it's bitter cold year around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms won't bloom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will! I was a hopeless\Nthug and dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I lived on and was able to\Nhave a profound change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every human in this world can be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to prove it here in Drum,\Nthe land where I was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. What you're trying to do\Nisn't medical science or any science.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the cherry blossoms bloom,\Nit will do nothing to human bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiriluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! We're alike. So I will\Nat least teach you before I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there's nothing\Nimpossible in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you can do anything, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the story of these two\Ndoesn't have a happy ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you...\Nthe miracle cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:23:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy. Are you really\Nlistening to-- Hey, where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I wonder if he's chasing\NTony-kun again... He's refusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to make him join us\Nand become our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just what you want, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... I wonder if there's\Nany medicine that works on fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hiriluk's Cherry Blossoms\NAnd The Will That Gets Carried On!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
